WEBVTT

00:09.340 --> 00:11.900
AAH! [ GASPS ]
[ CHUCKLES ]

00:11.940 --> 00:13.168
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]
WHAT'S THE MATI'ER?

00:13.210 --> 00:15.906
I-I JUST --
I DIDN'T HEAR YOU COME TO BED.

00:15.940 --> 00:17.043
OH,
THAT'S A GOOD THING.

00:17.080 --> 00:21.369
I-I-I SLEPT ON THE COUCH.
I DIDN'T WANT TO WAKE YOU.

00:21.420 --> 00:24.878
I'M, UH -- I'M ABOUT
TO MAKE YOU BREAKFAST.

00:24.920 --> 00:26.888
HEY, WHAT --
I DON'T KNOW. JUST...

00:26.920 --> 00:30.378
WELL, THERE'S NO RUSH.
RIGHT?

00:30.430 --> 00:32.591
NOW THAT
WE'RE BOTH AWAKE...

00:32.630 --> 00:33.858
[ GROANS ]

00:33.900 --> 00:35.856
HMM?
I'M SORRY.

00:35.900 --> 00:37.265
I'M JUST --
I'M -- I'M NOT...

00:37.300 --> 00:41.031
THERE'S JUST A LOT
GOING ON RIGHT NOW.

00:41.070 --> 00:42.958
YOU MEAN OLIVER
AND THE BOMBING ALLEGATIONS?

00:43.010 --> 00:45.103
YOU KNOW ABOUT THAT?

00:45.140 --> 00:47.836
I GOT A CALL
THIS MORNING.

00:47.880 --> 00:49.302
YEAH? FROM WHO?

00:49.350 --> 00:51.568
THE WHOLE DIVISION'S
TALKING ABOUT IT, YOU KNOW?

00:51.610 --> 00:54.738
NO ONE CAN BELIEVE IT, A GUY
LIKE HIM GOING DOWN LIKE THAT.

00:54.780 --> 00:56.418
[ CLICKS TONGUE ]
MAN.

00:56.450 --> 00:58.884
YOU DON'T THINK
HE DID IT?

00:58.920 --> 01:01.457
NO. OF COURSE NOT.

01:01.490 --> 01:04.789
BUT IT MUST BE PRETTY SERIOUS
IF I.A. IS LOOKING INTO IT.

01:04.830 --> 01:07.594
AND HIS, UM...
HIS KEY CARD

01:07.630 --> 01:10.121
WAS USED
TO ACCESS THE EVIDENCE ROOM.

01:10.170 --> 01:11.819
ANYBODY COULD HAVE USED
HIS KEY CARD.

01:11.870 --> 01:12.837
OH, YEAH.

01:12.870 --> 01:16.465
I MEAN, IT'S -- I'M SURE
IT'S A MISUNDERSTANDING.

01:16.510 --> 01:19.604
IT'S -- YOU KNOW,
IT'S OLIVER, RIGHT?

01:19.640 --> 01:22.438
HE'S ONE OF US.

01:22.480 --> 01:25.040
[ JEREMY FISHER'S
"UH-OH" PLAYS ]

01:25.080 --> 01:27.275
[ WATER RUNNING ]

01:32.360 --> 01:34.385
* YOU CAN'T PROVE IT

01:34.420 --> 01:35.318
* UH-OH

01:35.360 --> 01:36.782
* YOU GOT NOTHING LEGIT

01:36.830 --> 01:38.058
* UH-OH

01:38.090 --> 01:39.523
* THE GLOVE DON'T FIT

01:39.560 --> 01:40.720
* UH-OH

01:40.760 --> 01:42.193
* YOU GOT TO ACQUIT
IS THAT MY PHONE?

01:42.230 --> 01:43.424
YEP.
* UH-OH

01:43.470 --> 01:46.189
MY E-MAIL'S NOT WORKING, SO I,
UH, SENT YOU A TEST E-MAIL.

01:46.240 --> 01:47.798
* THAT'S ALL*YL?HU'ICJIFI GONNA GET

01:47.840 --> 01:49.865
I WAS JUST CHECKING TO SEE IF
IT WENT THROUGH, AND IT DIDN'T.

01:49.910 --> 01:50.968
HERE.

01:51.010 --> 01:52.034
