01:52.070 --> 01:54.334
DON'T GET MAD AT ME
IF THERE'S NO HOT WATER LEFI'.

01:54.380 --> 01:55.472
* YOU CAN'T PROVE IT

01:55.510 --> 01:56.807
[ SIREN WAILS ]
* UH-OH

01:56.850 --> 01:58.602
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

01:58.650 --> 02:01.118
* YOU'RE NEVER,
EVER GONNA PROVE IT *

