WE ARRESTED
YOUR BOYFRIEND.

37:12.760 --> 37:18.619
* OOH, OOH, OOH, OOH, OOH
* MM-MMM, MM-MMM,
MM-MMM, MM-MMM, MM-MMM *

37:20.530 --> 37:21.497
[ DOOR BUZZES ]

37:22.440 --> 37:25.261
ONCE YOU GET HIM DOWNTOWN,
KEEP THE CUFFS ON.

37:25.310 --> 37:27.107
YOU SON OF A BITCH.
I'LL BE OUT BY MORNING.

37:27.140 --> 37:28.402
I'LL HAVE YOUR BADGE.
YEAH.

37:28.440 --> 37:29.668
WELL, I'LL HAVE
PECK'S STATEMENT,

37:29.710 --> 37:32.577
SO LET'S SEE
HOW THAT PLAYS OUT.

37:32.610 --> 37:33.702
YOU SAY
I'M NOT A REAL COP, HUH?

37:33.750 --> 37:35.411
WHAT KIND OF COP ARE YOU?!
EASY, MOORE.

37:35.450 --> 37:38.783
YOU FOOL. CAN'T YOU SEE
THEY USED YOU TO GET TO ME?

37:38.820 --> 37:41.118
I KNOW THAT.

37:41.150 --> 37:46.326
OKAY, BUT HERE'S THE THING --
I WOULD HAVE DONE IT ANYWAY.

37:46.360 --> 37:49.921
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

37:49.960 --> 37:53.794
[ SIREN CHIRPING ]

37:53.830 --> 37:55.536
[ SIREN WAILS ]

38:00.240 --> 38:02.777
[ DOOR BUZZES, BEEPS ]

38:05.980 --> 38:08.073
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

38:08.110 --> 38:11.216
I JUMPED IN
WITH BOTH FEET.

38:11.250 --> 38:13.081
I GAVE YOU
A KEY TO MY PLACE.

38:13.120 --> 38:16.112
I LET YOU
INTO MY LIFE.

38:16.160 --> 38:19.789
I LET YOU LOOK
AFTER MY SON.

38:22.360 --> 38:23.554
I WON'T BE
AT YOUR TRIAL.

38:23.600 --> 38:25.192
I'M NOT GONNA COME
AND VISIT YOU,

38:25.230 --> 38:29.189
SO PLEASE DON'T CONTACT ME
EVER AGAIN.

38:29.240 --> 38:31.538
LOOK, TRACI...

38:32.210 --> 38:34.007
NO.
THIS IS WHERE IT ENDS.

38:34.040 --> 38:35.337
[ DOOR BUZZES, BEEPS ]

38:35.380 --> 38:37.803
[ SIGHS ]
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

38:37.840 --> 38:41.344
HEY.
HEY.

38:41.380 --> 38:44.269
UH, SO, I -- I THOUGHT
ABOUT WHAT YOU SAID.

38:44.320 --> 38:46.743
OH, YEAH?

38:46.790 --> 38:48.348
GOOD.

38:48.390 --> 38:51.484
MNH. NOT GOOD.

38:51.530 --> 38:53.953
I CAN'T
JUST BE FRIENDS WITH YOU.

38:57.130 --> 39:01.089
I'M SORRY. I CAN'T.

39:07.670 --> 39:09.171
YOU KNOW.

39:09.210 --> 39:11.371
FIRST OFF,
I CAN EXPLAIN.

39:11.410 --> 39:13.970
I MEAN, I HAD NO IDEA
SHE WAS YOUR WIFE --

39:14.010 --> 39:15.716
SHUT UP AND SIT DOWN.

39:17.550 --> 39:20.781
NOW, JAMIE AND I HAVEN'T BEEN
HAPPY FOR A LONG TIME.

39:20.820 --> 39:22.788
SHE'S AN ADDICT, DIAZ,
BUT YOU KNOW THAT.

39:22.820 --> 39:25.027
I'M -- I'M RECOVERED.
WELL, SHE'S NOT.

39:25.060 --> 39:28.951
SEE, NINE YEARS NOW, I'VE
WATCHED HER SLOWLY KILL HERSELF,

39:29.000 --> 39:30.092
AND I WANTED TO LEAVE,

39:30.130 --> 39:34.021
BUT I WAS AFRAID IT WOULD
SEND HER ON A DOWNWARD SPIRAL.

39:34.070 --> 39:36.698
WELL, NOT ANYMORE.

39:36.740 --> 39:38.332
SEE, I'M MOVING IN
WITH MY GIRLFRIEND.

39:38.370 --> 39:42.272
YOUR...GIRLFRIEND?

39:42.310 --> 39:45.677
I'M STARTING A NEW LIFE,
DIAZ...

39:45.710 --> 39:48.941
WHICH MEANS YOU'RE FREE
TO SEE JAMIE ANYTIME YOU WANT.

39:48.980 --> 39:50.868
JUST BE CAREFUL.

39:50.920 --> 39:51.944
I MEAN,
YOU SEEM LIKE A NICE GUY.

39:51.990 --> 39:56.859
JAMIE HAS A WAY OF DIGGING IN
AND NOT LETTING GO.

40:03.700 --> 40:06.225
* WHY AM I AFI-ITEAYID TO BE FREE?

40:06.270 --> 40:08.761
THANKS FOR
YOUR HELP TODAY.

40:08.800 --> 40:11.360
LOOK, YOU CAN THINK
WHAT YOU LIKE ABOUT I.A. --

40:11.400 --> 40:13.129
OR ABOUT ME,
FOR THAT MATTER,

40:13.170 --> 40:14.876
BUT DON'T YOU DARE
TRY TO PRETEND

40:14.910 --> 40:18.334
THAT WHAT I DO IS ANYTHING LESS
THAN GOOD DIFFICULT POLICE WORK.

40:18.380 --> 40:19.347
* WHY AM I AFRAID TO BE FREE?

40:19.380 --> 40:20.642
AND AS FAR
AS I'M CONCERNED,

40:20.680 --> 40:22.375
I THINK IT TAKES
A LOT MORE INTEGRITY

40:22.420 --> 40:23.318
TO GO AI-TER
CORRUPT COPS

40:23.350 --> 40:25.443
THAN JUST TO PRETEND
LIKE THEY DON'T EXIST.

40:25.490 --> 40:27.788
* FROM YOU

40:27.820 --> 40:30.983
* FROM YOU

40:31.020 --> 40:33.580
* I'M GONNA BURN IT DOWN
HEY, THERE, OUTLAW.

40:33.630 --> 40:35.757
AH, NOELLE WILLIAMS.
[ CHUCKLES ]

40:35.800 --> 40:38.325
YOU SIT RIGHT HERE.
THIS IS YOUR SEAT.

40:38.360 --> 40:40.066
THANK YOU.
BUY YOU A DRINK?

40:40.100 --> 40:42.933
NO, THANK YOU. I, UH --
I REACHED MY LIMIT...

40:42.970 --> 40:45.006
OH.
...LIKE MAYBE
FOUR HOURS AGO.

40:45.040 --> 40:46.029
[ LAUGHS ]

40:46.070 --> 40:49.676
I GUESS YOU HEARD ABOUT, UH,
STEVE PECK AND ALONSO.

40:49.710 --> 40:52.201
YEAH.
YEAH, I TALKED TO SAM.

40:52.250 --> 40:54.810
SEEMS LIKE YOU'RE GONNA HAVE
YOUR HANDS FULL FOR A WHILE.

40:54.850 --> 40:58.115
YEAH, WELL, IT'S TOO EARLY
TO TELL WHAT IT MEANS YET --

40:58.150 --> 40:59.788
EXCEPT WHEN IT COMES
TO YOU.

40:59.820 --> 41:01.344
OBVIOUSLY,
YOU'VE BEEN CLEARED

41:01.390 --> 41:02.982
OF ANY CONNECTION
TO THE BOMBING.

41:04.730 --> 41:07.949
WHICH MEANS --
WHICH MEANS WHAT?

41:07.990 --> 41:13.428
WHICH MEANS YOU CAN COME BACK
TO WORK, FREE AND CLEAR.

41:13.470 --> 41:18.032
AND IN CASE YOU DO NOT GET
AN OFFICIAL APOLOGY,

41:18.070 --> 41:24.100
FOR WHATEVER IT'S WORTH,
I'M SORRY...FOR ALL OF IT.

41:24.140 --> 41:26.040
YEAH,
WELL, THANK YOU.

41:26.080 --> 41:28.776
AND COMING FROM YOU,
IT'S WORTH A HELL OF A LOT.

41:28.820 --> 41:31.243
* I'M GONNA BURN IT DOWN

41:31.280 --> 41:33.248
Sam: HEY.
HMM?

41:33.290 --> 41:35.383
YOU DID GOOD TODAY.

41:35.420 --> 41:38.116
* FROM THE ASHES TO THE CROWN

41:38.160 --> 41:40.048
I DON'T FEEL LIKE IT.

41:40.090 --> 41:43.821
I FEEL LIKE I JUST RUINED
A BUNCH OF PEOPLE'S LIVES.

41:43.860 --> 41:45.828
THEIR LIVES
WERE RUINED ALREADY.

41:45.870 --> 41:47.929
THEY JUST
DIDN'T KNOW IT YET.

41:47.970 --> 41:49.835
IT'S UPSETTING.

41:49.870 --> 41:51.838
YOU KNOW, TRACI DIDN'T KNOW
THAT STEVE WAS BAD.

41:51.870 --> 41:53.963
WELL, IN MY OPINION,
STEVE WASN'T BAD.

41:54.010 --> 41:57.036
HE JUST DID A BAD THING
AND THEN ANOTHER BAD THING

41:57.080 --> 41:59.708
AND THEN ANOTHER,
AND THAT'S HOW IT GOES.

41:59.750 --> 42:02.913
[ SIGHS ]
I JUST WANT TO GO HOME.

42:02.950 --> 42:05.418
I WANT TO GET INTO P.J.s
AND SIT ON THE COUCH

42:05.450 --> 42:07.384
AND BE COMPLETELY
BORING WITH YOU.

42:07.420 --> 42:11.254
* SAVE MYSELF NOW

42:11.290 --> 42:12.882
I GOT NEWS FOR YOU.

42:16.400 --> 42:16.923
* SAVE MYSELF NOW
